message:
Dedicated Law Enforcement and Prosecutors work tirelessly to obtain justice for individuals who have been victimized by human traffickers. 
"As this case demonstrates, sex trafficking is a cruel and callous business, in which violence and threats are often used to control victims. It’s our duty to hold traffickers such as Mr. Lewis accountable for the horrendous acts they commit.“
#makingadifference

attachments.media_description: Teen Girls Rescued, Violent Human Trafficker Gets Lengthy Prison Sentence - San Bernardino County District Attorney
